Name":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-12T17:34:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have moved your question to the Gameplay subforum, so now you know where that is. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EWhat kind of trouble did you have reaching orbit? Ship design or piloting?\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"paul_c","CreatedById":208135,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-12T17:47:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223939366\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200960\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615562264\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210553\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Harald Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Harald Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalso... 2:00\u003Csup\u003Epm\u003C/sup\u003E to 4:00\u003Csup\u003Epm\u003C/sup\u003E and 6:00\u003Csup\u003Epm\u003C/sup\u003E to morning, i am not here\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand time to eat not (also, in american south time)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223939396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200960\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615567968\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210553\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Harald Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n52 minutes ago, Harald Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncan u give me the link for the chat???????\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:happy:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/happy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:happy:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease be aware (or learn) how forums work. Forum is NOT chat, and neither is \u0022chat\u0022 necessary to solve your problem. Neither are people going to fall over themselves trying to help you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo...to start.....what have you done already to try reach orbit?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-12T20:42:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223939421\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200960\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615571275\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208135\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022paul_c\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, paul_c said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease be aware (or learn) how forums work. Forum is NOT chat, and neither is \u0022chat\u0022 necessary to solve your problem. Neither are people going to fall over themselves trying to help you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve seen people here fall over themselves to help others. We\u0027re a pretty nice bunch. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anonymous49","CreatedById":209341,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-13T07:26:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUse \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Mechjeb (mod)\u0022\u003EMJ\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-13T12:36:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223939364\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200960\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615561658\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210553\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Harald Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, Harald Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI AM SO NOOB THAT I DIDN\u0027T GET IN ORBIT IN CAEER MODE\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t worry, you\u0027re in lots of good company-- KSP is \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ehard\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E, at first.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ECould you tell us a little bit about what happens?\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u00A0 Specifically:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nCould you show us a picture of your ship?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nWhen your ship reaches 10 km altitude, how fast is it going?\u00A0 And what direction is it pointed?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAny description of how you\u0027re flying your ship and what happens would be helpful.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s how to post a picture, if you don\u0027t know:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nTake a screenshot in the game (F1 by default; the game will put it in the \u0022Screenshots\u0022 folder of wherever you have KSP installed)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nUpload your screenshot to some free image-sharing service, such as \u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAfter you\u0027ve uploaded it, right-click on the image in your browser and choose \u0022Copy Image Location\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPaste that URL here in your forum post and we can see the picture \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"king of nowhere","CreatedById":204876,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-13T15:34:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhave you tried playing the tutorial? there are some good tutorials in the game that should teach you to get to orbit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-13T16:25:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSufficient deltav \u002B sufficient thrust - detrimental\u00A0drag \u002B understanding circularising technique = orbit success.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDeltaV = enough to get into orbit (figure eludes me but about 3-3.5k maybe?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThrust = more than 1 \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Thrust-to-weight ratio\u0022\u003Etwr\u003C/abbr\u003E at surface of kerbin, I like about 1.75 myself as I\u0027m impatient and used to Tantares engines.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDrag = use fairings to stop draggy parts at top of rocket and fins at bottom to add it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTechnique = burn prograde at the apoapsis to increase periapsis and form a \u2018circle\u2019. Also doing a gravity turn means you can reduce \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E, lots of youtube vids to explain this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne or more of those is stopping you I\u2019d wager.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Harald Kerbal","CreatedById":210553,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-20T15:20:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnow i did fly 2 satelites (not as once) in eart\u0027s (KERBIN) orbit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-20T18:41:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223942835\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200960\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221616253658\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210553\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Harald Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Harald Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnow i did fly 2 satelites (not as once) in eart\u0027s (KERBIN) orbit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCongrats. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}